Package: rctbayespower
Title: Bayesian Power Analysis for Randomized Controlled Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package provides tools for conducting Bayesian power analysis
    for randomized controlled trials using brms and Stan. It allows researchers
    to estimate power curves, determine optimal sample sizes, and assess the
    probability of detecting treatment effects under various scenarios.
